result.title: what is your patient percentage on detecting your wrong answer case ?
result.content: Hello Codeforces, Recently i face a problem that when a problem is judged wrong answer i can't wait to detect the wronged the test case by my self and i use the jury's answers. a) what is the time u spend on detecting the wronged answer by your self ? b) average time before u use the tutorial of the problem ? Thanks , :)
